{"tid":1242980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又不顧北京反對 加拿大軍艦高調穿越台海","createTime":"2019-06-19T09:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T00:20:32.000Z","uid":141151,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c2dc0c10698b71bc3f3db98a8333a3b813b1c758","tid":1242980,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"又不顧北京反對 加拿大軍艦高調穿越台海<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/06/19/897577.html?code=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F897577.html%3Fcode%3Db5&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=5b2df2f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/06/19/897577.html?code=b5</a><br />\n<br />\n【看中國2019年6月19日訊】繼美國軍艦今年起每月行經台灣海峽之後，加拿大皇家海軍軍艦也加入行列了！根據國外網站圖資顯示，加拿大皇家海軍的哈利法克斯級巡防艦「里賈納」號，在18日的凌晨由南向北穿越台海，而且她在航行時，一度打開「船舶自動辨識系統」（AIS）。<br />\n<br />\n《LTN》根據「MarineTraffic」網站資訊顯示，「里賈納」號（HMCS Regina）最後現蹤時間為18日凌晨0時左右，地點位於台灣西北部的海域。<br />\n<br />\n而「里賈納」號是加國海軍哈利法克斯級巡防艦第五號艦，其滿載排水量超過4500噸，並搭載魚叉反艦飛彈、「RIM-162」防空飛彈、反潛魚雷、方陣快砲等武器，戰力相當均衡，同時也是加國海軍的主力作戰艦艇。<br />\n<br />\n據日本海上自衛隊的資訊，「里賈納」號在6月13日至15日期間，跟日本海上自衛隊船艦在南海和越南外海進行「KAEDEX19-1」聯合操演。<br />\n<br />\n當時日本派出三艘護衛艦，而加拿大皇家海軍除「里賈納」號外，「阿斯提利斯」號補給艦也投入此次演訓，藉此提高日本海上自衛隊戰力與跨國合作機制。<br />\n<br />\n事實上自今年起，美國海軍每月20日以後都會派二艘軍艦編隊穿越台海，其編隊模式包含二艘伯克級的神盾驅逐艦、一驅逐艦一補給艦、一驅逐艦跟一海岸防衛隊巡防艦等。"},{"pid":"6b1b1e120b8562f43bdc8d7ebbd61494ad774634","tid":1242980,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef39912d9ea336e2f5bb4b60f34536dfc571d41","tid":1242980,"uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:23:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>美國、英國、加拿大、日本、越南、澳洲、菲律賓、法國等<span style=\"color: red;\">至少八國</span>軍艦都在南海繞來繞去</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f6fba8833eb92098cdc2f2e1a7073f844d91962d","tid":1242980,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4fb8e40110719e36b7a224e2f4d17b47705aa0","tid":1242980,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac8d125a9f8f36a9c08523412d38e2fac9024fc","tid":1242980,"uid":127751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:45:37.000Z","msg":"解放香港"},{"pid":"a7772e97018f6de4e17efc787add7cadb278a593","tid":1242980,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"你咪反對囉<br />\n睇死你得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明知共產黨根本冇得武力解放台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05830d57da5fe09b6b5ca5f59965e4cfb28ddb9","tid":1242980,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20794c1ad39aaa5be89717624e3c7fce5eff289","tid":1242980,"uid":119347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:13:21.000Z","msg":"加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4655082708e5edc87012f9ef8518237c3be676","tid":1242980,"uid":209248